oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Eddy Arnold Show - #951 - Incomplete take
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: An incomplete take of the Eddy Arnold Show #951, produced and transcribed in Nashville, TN. by Brown Radio Productions. Featuring Eddy Arnold and the Tennessee Plowboys, the Willis Brothers (introduced as the Oklahoma Wranglers), Roy Wiggins, Skeeter Willis and host Vince Harding. Opening theme music, 'Cattle Call'; closing theme music, 'Cattle Call'.
